From: Colin Ian King <colin.i.king@gmail.com>
Date: Mon, 7 Mar 2022 22:24:29 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] mt76: connac: make read-only array ba_range static const
Git-commit: c00e13726b6c728370686b6d6e0e71b0a9f37f03
